msgid ""
"Run `migrate-dek --dry-run` and confirm zero remaining `v1` rows. Any `v1` "
"ciphertext encountered after a KEK rotation is unrecoverable: it is pinned "
"to the old `token_secret` and not protected by a DEK at all."
msgstr ""

